
Make cmpiOSBase_HelloProvider
$ make

make sample client
$ make test

Remote Method Invoke
$ ./hello (サーバ側のスクリプトのパス)
( sample 
[masa@miami sfpro]$ ./hello /usr/local/share/konoha/sample/fib.k

----------------------------------------------------------
Testing invokeMethod() ...
+++T1:passing IN chars argument
invokeMethod() rc=0, msg=(null)
return value:[fib(36): 14930352]

)
Regist to sfcb
$ sudo sh /usr/share/sblim-cmpi-base/provider-register.sh -v -r mof/Linux_Hello.registration -m mof/Linux_Hello.mof

UnRegist from sfcb
$ sudo sh /usr/share/sblim-cmpi-base/provider-register.sh -v -r mof/Linux_Hello.registration -m mof/Linux_Hello.mof -d

How to Get Instance
$ wbemcli gi 'http://masa:konoha@localhost:5988/root/cimv2:Linux_Hello.Name="world"'


